input.command:
sqlite3 "/Users/david/workspace/claude-code-claimdb/test_dbs/european_football_2.sqlite" "
SELECT p.player_name, 
       CAST(SUM(pa.heading_accuracy) AS REAL) / COUNT(pa.player_fifa_api_id) AS avg_heading_accuracy
FROM Player p
JOIN Player_Attributes pa ON p.player_fifa_api_id = pa.player_fifa_api_id
WHERE p.player_name IN ('Michael Ballack', 'Fernando Llorente', 'John Terry', 'Naldo', 'Per Mertesacker', 'Luca Toni', 'Didier Drogba', 'Miroslav Klose', 'Daniel Van Buyten', 'Fernando Morientes')
GROUP BY p.player_name
ORDER BY avg_heading_accuracy ASC;
"
